{"id": 1606, "genre": 1001, "title": "虽说在共享社会，但有哪些分享会让你觉得…还是算了吧？", "description": "对方没有理你，并向你扔了一只表情……你也是一个分享的时候心理压力很大的人吗？（题图：K Whiteford）", "record_count": 3969, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201704020715217byI28o5Ypen9Cjd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-06T03:00:09Z", "options": [{"id": 189184, "content": "所有的，私人用品，都无法共享。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996719}, {"id": 190208, "content": "共享账号.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905472}, {"id": 188929, "content": "书，没钱吗，自己买不行吗…非得借我的看…然后还不爱惜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979496}, {"id": 189185, "content": "公共马桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996715}, {"id": 194817, "content": "共享单车\n结果自行车多了一倍\n这样真环保吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660406}, {"id": 189186, "content": "分享他的个人主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996755}, {"id": 188932, "content": "不想接受烂片，烂音乐，以及对方的私生活，我又不是老妈子，有什么问题自己解决吧好吗？要不要当个成年人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993862}, {"id": 191492, "content": "艺术品味与审美和价值观", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991400}, {"id": 189189, "content": "分享所谓的成功经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992251}, {"id": 189445, "content": "朋友向单身的自己分享自己的爱情经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997376}, {"id": 188934, "content": "我说萝卜好吃，可是大部分人觉得白菜好吃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969279}, {"id": 188935, "content": "My Phone!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995853}, {"id": 189703, "content": "悲伤的爱情歌曲，身临其境时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998031}, {"id": 188936, "content": "即使是很好的朋友也有自己的私人空间自己的秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995848}, {"id": 189704, "content": "就差你一个赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998031}, {"id": 189193, "content": "大概是我觉得什么惊艳了我的世界而你觉得是炫耀吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996781}, {"id": 189449, "content": "我的大学生活过得咋这么悲催  孤独唉～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997380}, {"id": 188939, "content": "无休止的晒孩子最受不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955405}, {"id": 189196, "content": "csgo开箱子出一把屠夫 “哎老哥借我玩两天！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993605}, {"id": 189197, "content": "凡事私人空间，都应不被共享", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995435}, {"id": 188943, "content": "其实想说，共享和分享是两个概念诶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375024}, {"id": 197137, "content": "会有很大的压力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016135}, {"id": 188945, "content": "对女权的看法还是算了吧，大家保留各自看法还能做朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988845}, {"id": 188946, "content": "有些心情是不能分享的，分享了也不一定有人会懂！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993737}, {"id": 188947, "content": "所有想分享到朋友圈的东西都…还是算了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786145}, {"id": 188949, "content": "我觉得共享还得要看对象是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994720}, {"id": 194325, "content": "设了很多次分组，依然不知道该怎么设才能把喜爱的东西分享给对的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009185}, {"id": 189463, "content": "分享太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731597}, {"id": 190743, "content": "炫耀似的分享，或者说所有让我感觉到有炫耀感的分享，都不太喜欢，一般不太接受别人的分享，也不去主动分享什么，对我来说分享就是请求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001890}, {"id": 193559, "content": "别拿你的CF和我武装突袭比  求你了哥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007427}, {"id": 188952, "content": "共享虽好，但不会被人珍惜吧(>_<)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986568}, {"id": 189464, "content": "一楼和四楼 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869548}, {"id": 189209, "content": "不要把自己的生活全部都发说说发朋友圈！！！！！真的特么不想看！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996903}, {"id": 188954, "content": "还是喜欢是一个物品的所有者，但是这好像的确会造成资源浪费。现在的共享单车就真的挺实用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995874}, {"id": 189211, "content": "分享自己很痛苦的经历来寻得安慰，，，，负能量满满当当", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858403}, {"id": 188956, "content": "自己正在看手机别人伸头过来一块看。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995882}, {"id": 188957, "content": "思维方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978930}, {"id": 188958, "content": "QQ空间的说说...一条以上的都不能理解 心情好了坏了 天气阴了晴了 各种事都要晾出来说一说 实在不能理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995885}, {"id": 188959, "content": "每次在朋友圈晒点什么，总有人泼冷水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995890}, {"id": 189983, "content": "工资吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976643}, {"id": 200480, "content": "快被说音乐电影等等其他艺术了，我恨不得全世界和我的审美品牌同步率80%以上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258853}, {"id": 188960, "content": "单车，用完放好不行就得放人行道盲道上", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883848}, {"id": 189984, "content": "心灵鸡汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986297}, {"id": 192802, "content": "品味...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980278}, {"id": 188963, "content": "天天秀恩爱的，动不动苹果了，过个节晒花，还有就是晒孩子的，点点滴滴都放朋友圈了，好尴尬，真想删了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995909}, {"id": 188964, "content": "自己的觀點", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145815}, {"id": 188965, "content": "一个自己感觉搞笑的段子发到群里，沉了……难道我笑点这么奇特？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959559}, {"id": 189989, "content": "老婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984004}, {"id": 188966, "content": "己所不欲，勿施于人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995920}, {"id": 188967, "content": "心情、音乐、书籍与电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995915}]}